SELECT 
  t1.id,
  t1.payment_method

FROM raw_payments AS t1, raw_orders AS t2

WHERE t1.order_id = t2.id or t2.status IS NOT NULL or t1.payment_method IS NOT NULL

SELECT 
    RAND() as c_float, GENERATE_UUID() as c_string, 
    GENERATE_ARRAY(1, 4, 10) as c_array, GENERATE_DATE_ARRAY('2016-10-05', '2016-10-08') as c_date_array 
from `prophecy-qa.qa_test_dataset.all_type_table` 
where c_int64 != (select count(*) from tpcds_1_env_uitesting_shared) limit 100
